&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;You will&amp;nbsp;operate&amp;nbsp;at the intersection of device development, drug product, and external partner execution, with direct impact on product quality, program timelines, and patient experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Roles and Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
